# TMDB API credentials
# 1. Create a free account at https://www.themoviedb.org/
# 2. Go to Settings -> API and request an API key (choose "Developer").
# 3. Copy the "API Read Access Token" (a long v4 Bearer token) below.
#
# NOTE: Anything prefixed with EXPO_PUBLIC_ is embedded in the app bundle and is
# therefore extractable by users. This is acceptable for local development of a
# read-only feed. Before a public release, move TMDB calls behind a thin proxy
# (e.g. a Cloudflare Worker) and keep the token server-side.
EXPO_PUBLIC_TMDB_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_tmdb_v4_read_access_token_here

